---
import DocsLayout from "../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro";
---

<DocsLayout>
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-white">
    <section class="text-center mb-12 p-8 bg-linear-to-r from-cyan-950/40 to-blue-950/40 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/20 backdrop-blur-sm">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-3 bg-linear-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-400 bg-clip-text">
        Astro + Tailwind CSS Installation
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-body/80">
        Complete guide to set up Astro with Tailwind CSS in your project
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-6 mb-12">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 sm:gap-6 bg-neutral-secondary-soft p-6 rounded-lg border border-default hover:border-cyan-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-cyan-500/10 group">
        <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 text-white font-bold text-2xl rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          1
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Create a new Astro project</h2>
          <p class="text-body/80 mb-4">
            Run the following command to create a new Astro project:
          </p>
          <div class="bg-black/50 text-cyan-300 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-cyan-500 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto">
            <code>npm create astro@latest my-project</code>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 bg-blue-950/30 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-blue-200 text-sm">
              üí° Follow the interactive instructions to configure your project. Select the options that best suit your needs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 sm:gap-6 bg-neutral-secondary-soft p-6 rounded-lg border border-default hover:border-cyan-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-cyan-500/10 group">
        <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 text-white font-bold text-2xl rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          2
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Navigate to project directory</h2>
          <p class="text-body/80 mb-4">Navigate to your project folder:</p>
          <div class="bg-black/50 text-cyan-300 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-cyan-500 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto">
            <code>cd my-project</code>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 sm:gap-6 bg-neutral-secondary-soft p-6 rounded-lg border border-default hover:border-cyan-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-cyan-500/10 group">
        <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 text-white font-bold text-2xl rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          3
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Install Tailwind CSS</h2>
          <p class="text-body/80 mb-4">
            Use the official Astro command to install and configure Tailwind CSS automatically:
          </p>
          <div class="bg-black/50 text-cyan-300 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-cyan-500 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto">
            <code>npx astro add tailwind</code>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 bg-blue-950/30 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-blue-200 text-sm mb-3">üí° This command does the following automatically:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-body/80 text-sm">
                <span class="text-green-400 font-bold mt-0.5">‚úì</span>
                <span>Installs the necessary packages: <code class="bg-black/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-cyan-300">tailwindcss</code> and <code class="bg-black/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-cyan-300">autoprefixer</code></span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-body/80 text-sm">
                <span class="text-green-400 font-bold mt-0.5">‚úì</span>
                <span>Creates the Tailwind configuration file: <code class="bg-black/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-cyan-300">tailwind.config.mjs</code></span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-body/80 text-sm">
                <span class="text-green-400 font-bold mt-0.5">‚úì</span>
                <span>Creates the global CSS file: <code class="bg-black/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-cyan-300">src/globals.css</code></span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-body/80 text-sm">
                <span class="text-green-400 font-bold mt-0.5">‚úì</span>
                <span>Updates the Astro configuration</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 sm:gap-6 bg-neutral-secondary-soft p-6 rounded-lg border border-default hover:border-cyan-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-cyan-500/10 group">
        <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 text-white font-bold text-2xl rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          4
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Configure Tailwind CSS (Optional)</h2>
          <p class="text-body/80 mb-4">
            Edit the <code class="bg-black/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-cyan-300">tailwind.config.mjs</code> file if you need to customize Tailwind:
          </p>
          <div class="bg-black/50 text-cyan-300 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-cyan-500 font-mono text-xs sm:text-sm overflow-x-auto">
            <pre class="text-cyan-300"><code>{`/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */ 
 export default {
  content: ['./src/**/*.{astro,html,js,jsx,md,mdx,svelte,ts,tsx,vue}'],
  theme: {
    extend: {
      colors: {
        custom: '#1a1a1a',
      },
    },
  },
  plugins: [],
            }`}</code></pre>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 sm:gap-6 bg-neutral-secondary-soft p-6 rounded-lg border border-default hover:border-cyan-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-cyan-500/10 group">
        <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 text-white font-bold text-2xl rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          5
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Verify the installation</h2>
          <p class="text-body/80 mb-4">
            Start the development server to verify that everything works correctly:
          </p>
          <div class="bg-black/50 text-cyan-300 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-cyan-500 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto">
            <code>npm run dev</code>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 bg-blue-950/30 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-blue-200 text-sm">
              üí° Your project should be running at <code class="bg-black/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-cyan-300">http://localhost:4321</code>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 sm:gap-6 bg-neutral-secondary-soft p-6 rounded-lg border border-default hover:border-cyan-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-cyan-500/10 group">
        <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 text-white font-bold text-2xl rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          6
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Start using Tailwind</h2>
          <p class="text-body/80 mb-4">
            Now you can use Tailwind CSS classes in your Astro components:
          </p>
          <div class="bg-black/50 text-cyan-300 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-cyan-500 font-mono text-xs sm:text-sm overflow-x-auto">
            <pre class="text-cyan-300"><code>&lt;div class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen bg-linear-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-600"&gt;
  &lt;h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white"&gt;Hello Astro + Tailwind!&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-neutral-secondary-soft p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-lg border border-default mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-cyan-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
        </svg>
        Installation Verification
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <label class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-tertiary transition-colors cursor-pointer group">
          <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5 accent-cyan-500 cursor-pointer" />
          <span class="text-body/90 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Astro installed correctly</span>
        </label>
        <label class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-tertiary transition-colors cursor-pointer group">
          <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5 accent-cyan-500 cursor-pointer" />
          <span class="text-body/90 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Tailwind CSS integrated into the project</span>
        </label>
        <label class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-tertiary transition-colors cursor-pointer group">
          <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5 accent-cyan-500 cursor-pointer" />
          <span class="text-body/90 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">File <code class="bg-black/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-cyan-300">tailwind.config.mjs</code> present</span>
        </label>
        <label class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-tertiary transition-colors cursor-pointer group">
          <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5 accent-cyan-500 cursor-pointer" />
          <span class="text-body/90 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Development server running</span>
        </label>
        <label class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-tertiary transition-colors cursor-pointer group">
          <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5 accent-cyan-500 cursor-pointer" />
          <span class="text-body/90 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Tailwind classes working correctly</span>
        </label>
      </div>
    </section>

    
    <section class="bg-neutral-secondary-soft p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-lg border border-default mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Useful Commands</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-linear-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 p-5 rounded-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-200">
          <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3 text-sm">Start development server</h3>
          <code class="block bg-black/30 text-white px-3 py-2 rounded font-mono text-sm">npm run dev</code>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-linear-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 p-5 rounded-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-200">
          <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3 text-sm">Build for production</h3>
          <code class="block bg-black/30 text-white px-3 py-2 rounded font-mono text-sm">npm run build</code>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-linear-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 p-5 rounded-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-200">
          <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3 text-sm">Production preview</h3>
          <code class="block bg-black/30 text-white px-3 py-2 rounded font-mono text-sm">npm run preview</code>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-linear-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 p-5 rounded-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-200">
          <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3 text-sm">Check project</h3>
          <code class="block bg-black/30 text-white px-3 py-2 rounded font-mono text-sm">npx astro check</code>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-neutral-secondary-soft p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-lg border border-default mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Useful Resources</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-2xl">üîó</span>
          <a href="https://docs.astro.build" target="_blank" class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 hover:underline transition-colors">
            Official Astro Documentation
          </a>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-2xl">üîó</span>
          <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs" target="_blank" class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 hover:underline transition-colors">
            Official Tailwind CSS Documentation
          </a>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-2xl">üîó</span>
          <a href="https://docs.astro.build/en/guides/integrations-guide/tailwind/" target="_blank" class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 hover:underline transition-colors">
            Tailwind Integration in Astro
          </a>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-2xl">üîó</span>
          <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/blog/tailwindcss-v4" target="_blank" class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 hover:underline transition-colors">
            Tailwind CSS v4 News
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-neutral-secondary-soft p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-lg border border-default">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Troubleshooting</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="pb-6 border-b border-default">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">‚ùì Tailwind styles are not being applied</h3>
          <p class="text-body/80 leading-relaxed">
            Verify that the <code class="bg-black/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-cyan-300">content</code> configuration in <code class="bg-black/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-cyan-300">tailwind.config.mjs</code> includes the correct paths to your Astro files (.astro).
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="pb-6 border-b border-default">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">‚ùì Error during installation</h3>
          <p class="text-body/80 leading-relaxed">
            Try deleting the <code class="bg-black/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-cyan-300">node_modules</code> folder and the <code class="bg-black/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-cyan-300">package-lock.json</code> file, then run <code class="bg-black/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-cyan-300">npm install</code> again.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">‚ùì Tailwind classes are marked in red in the editor</h3>
          <p class="text-body/80 leading-relaxed">
            Install the official Tailwind CSS extension for VS Code to get autocomplete and intellisense.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>